{"title":"反差","authors":["池北偶江帆"],"dates":[{"year":1992,"month":2,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"反差"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"池北偶诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江帆画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿着漂亮衣衫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浑身时髦打扮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俨然一位“尖头鳗”*。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"外表虽然不凡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举止实在不堪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"其实是个无赖汉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"果皮到处乱扔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随地随便吐痰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不讲公德成习惯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满嘴脏话高声喊，“他妈的”是口头禅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"污染空气无忌惮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挤电车逞野蛮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抢座位争先占，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老弱病残全不管。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"剧场中侃大山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饭馆里敲杯盘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无理取闹专捣蛋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骂大街家常便饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打出手并非偶然，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"端的是不知羞惭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"*“尖头鳗”是英语“绅士”的译音。（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}